    "---\n",
    "<a id='module-0'></a>\n",
    "## Module 0 — SQL Exploratory Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "This module runs SQL queries using **DuckDB** — an in-process analytical SQL engine that runs on DataFrames without a server. \n",
    "\n",
    "**Business questions answered:**\n",
    "1. Which merchant categories generate the most fraud value — and what share of their total volume does that represent?\n",
    "2. Is fraud concentrated in specific hours of the day, or spread evenly?\n",
    "3. Which customer segments have the highest fraud exposure in dollar terms?\n",
    "4. Do high-risk merchants cluster by type, or is risk spread across the portfolio?\n",
    "5. Which accounts show velocity fraud signatures detectable with SQL alone?\n",
    "\n",
    "Each query ends with a plain-English business recommendation."
   ]
